Title: Another Round of Noodles
Description:
Back again for more noodles?

Very well, say the word and I will take you back to a version of history where you ran your own noodle stand.
ObjectivesText: Talk to Grandmaster Jakkus to complete the scenario Noodle Time.

Objectives.Text: Queue for a shift at the noodle stand through Grandmaster Jakkus
Complete a shift at the Halfhill noodle stand
